ðŸ“Œ OVERALL PURPOSE

This program demonstrates basic cybersecurity techniques such as password hashing, secure authentication, file protection, and access control. It is designed to help users understand how secure file systems work while providing a functional and interactive tool that protects sensitive data from unauthorized access.


